{"body": "a monkey-patched initializer to apply mysql strict mode to Rails 3.2:\n\n```ruby\nclass ActiveRecord::ConnectionAdapters::Mysql2Adapter\n\nprivate\n  alias_method :configure_connection_without_strict_mode, :configure_connection\n\n  def configure_connection\n    configure_connection_without_strict_mode\n    strict_mode = \"SQL_MODE='STRICT_ALL_TABLES'\"\n    execute(\"SET #{strict_mode}\", :skip_logging)\n  end\nend\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6702455", "created_at": "2012-07-02T07:59:15Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6069#issuecomment-6702455", "updated_at": "2012-07-02T07:59:27Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6069, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/mikhailov", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cffe91a6cc6e6ce8213ed575821dadf7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F050b8cbe360fb66fe566aae25cd800df.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/received_events", "gravatar_id": "cffe91a6cc6e6ce8213ed575821dadf7", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "mikhailov", "type": "User", "id": 14601, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mikhailov/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e89dabd354364b9010a75"}, "id": 6702455, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6069"}
